metadata.name: MagicHeart #1
metadata.description:
Big Eyes METAverse or BEMETA NFTs - a collection of beautiful, funny, bewitching, alluring, sexy, mischievous, exciting female eyes!

MagicHearts is a limited edition of 1,000 cute hearts, released especially for Valentine's Day.

Artworks is created and completely hand-drawn by @pink_dust ART.

By owning MagicHearts you become a lifetime member of the pink_dust ART Club and are on our whitelist, they give you the opportunity to have privileges on the giveaway and when minting our NFTs.
